{"tid":653738,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：良心學者的代價","createTime":"2018-05-05T03:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T13:02:24.000Z","uid":5843,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"326790ab773154a91d8256d5f2db0e51e7f1e520","tid":653738,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:58:58.000Z","msg":"陳雲：良心學者的代價，陳雲有版你睇。我揭穿政府的母語陰謀之後，面書封鎖我的著作。華夏聖言出版社的語文著作系列被面書封鎖，《粵語學中文》、《廣東雅言》及《香港城邦論（增訂本）》等著作被扣押，不能在商品欄目顯示出來。<br />\n讀者如要郵購（敝社會用快遞送達），仍可pm敝出版社的面書專頁聯絡。<br />\n(按：我已經無法在香港的大學教書，而中資書局封鎖大部分我的著作售賣。目前只能用二樓書店或網上直銷。另外，幾個朋友告知，我有一篇介紹廣東話的面書長帖文，被面書刪除了。）"},{"pid":"2de53a81c0018cdf1226d7bbdf4be633fc85dc62","tid":653738,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T10:25:08.000Z","msg":"陳雲好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾政府打壓"},{"pid":"16fe3656ba1d535e8397daaeb2c1dd2c23979d2b","tid":653738,"uid":119895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:02:24.000Z","msg":"國師又要清蟹貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}